Configure List

Configure List allows users to customize which columns appear in a list view and how records are displayed.

Features
Add or remove columns
Rearrange column order
Change list layout
Save personalized views
Benefits
Displays only required information
Improves productivity
Makes record management easier
Example

Right-click a list header → Configure → List Layout

🔹 Personalize List

Personalize List allows individual users to customize their own list view without affecting other users.

Features
Select visible columns
Hide unnecessary fields
Create personalized layouts
User-specific customization
Benefits
Better user experience
Faster navigation
Cleaner interface
Example

Open a list → Click Settings (Gear Icon) → Personalize List Columns

List Calculator

List Calculator performs calculations directly on numeric columns in list views.

Features
Calculates totals automatically
Supports aggregation functions
Works on selected records
Supported Calculations
Count
Sum
Average
Maximum
Minimum
Benefits
Quick data analysis
No need for external tools
Improves reporting efficiency
Example

Right-click numeric column → Show → Aggregate → Sum
